        <updateDate>2005-03-07T21:38:08Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Gold Restitution Act of 2005 - Amends the Bretton Woods Agreements Act to prohibit any U.S. director at the International Monetary Fund (IMF) voting for a proposal to sell or otherwise convert or liquidate gold unless certain conditions are met.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
